Great Oak Funding is a private lender focused on providing funding to help businesses grow and expand.  Great Oak Funding provides capital through mezzanine financing to existing companies with a track record of revenue.  Great Oak Funding's management team has a history of working with distressed companies to provide guidance and capital to move companies back to success.

The goal of Great Oak Funding is to create successful businesses that are adequately capitalized, and possess strong management skills, all while keeping a focus on maintaining strong ownership with the founders/owners. We accomplish this by working closely with business owners to help define their growth strategy while designing a plan to achieve those goals. Of course, one aspect of achieving success is having sufficient capital. Great Oak Funding reviews the prospective borrower's financials and then helps to build a strategy to adequately capitalize the company.

Advantages of working with Great Oak Funding :

•	Provides loans to companies with short-term capital needs;

•	Is an agile lender that makes quick decisions and can turn around loans in a short turnaround;

•	Uses a company's assets as a determinant for loans, as opposed to many lenders who require a predetermined amount of cash-flow to qualify for loans;

•	Considers alternative lending arrangements including non-traditional security terms and secure loan purchases and sale lease-backs.
